{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解库仑扭秤；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理解电荷间的相互作用力。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种电荷相互排斥，异种电荷相互吸引。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">库仑扭秤、带正电的小球。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.拖动带正电的小球接触扭秤上的金属环，使扭秤中小球带上电，观察转盘的刻度；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.点击带正电的小球，在属性中改变电量；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．重复步骤</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的操作，观察转盘的刻度。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电荷间的作用力与电荷间距离的平方成反比，与电荷量的乘积成正比</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">库仑定律：<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">F=kq</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub>1</sub></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">q</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub>2</sub></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">/r</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sup>2</sup>，</span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">k=</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">9.0&times;10<sup>9</sup>N&middot;m<sup>2</sup>/C<sup>2</sup>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}